reviewText: This is a dynamic, powerful DVD set that inspires the audience to be mindful of the words we use, and the power they have.  Love Joel Osteen and his teaching!

This is a great documentary! It's got celebrity guests and a soundtrack full of up-and-coming hip hop stars. Best of all, it's an uplifting story that shows the power of words, specifically the words of Jesus Christ. This is a great video for kids and adults.
